<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٣٠٥]</span> في <span class="c2">(ب)</span> ثم قام.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٣٠٦]</span> صف٢ /٣٠٣<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
